data.text:
The Rise and Fall of Nokia Mobile

With Nokia's innovations Finland was steered out of depression and into leadership of the cell phone world. What were the decisions that led to the demise of one of the most successful technological businesses of modern times? A story told from the perspective of the inventors and engineers who worked in the mobile phone business during it's heyday.

IMDb 7.01 h 31 min2017

13+
